      "span_text": "As previously reported for other non-IESs  , the endogenous sequences that were complementary to the introduced target sequence in the chimeric constructs were eliminated in some of the progeny ( Figures S6A and S6B, coDel) , indicating that ectopic expression of late-scnRNAs from the target loci occurred when these progenies were produced.",
